          <p>Most organizations know they have a problem long before they understand its root cause. We bring structured diagnostic frameworks — process mapping, data analysis, and stakeholder interviews — to cut through assumptions and pinpoint exactly where breakdowns are occurring and why.</p>
          <p>Once the diagnosis is clear, we work side by side with your team to design solutions that are practical, not theoretical. Every recommendation comes with defined owners, realistic timelines, and the success metrics you need to know whether the fix is working.</p>
          <p>Designing a solution is only half the job. We stay involved through the implementation phase, providing coaching, troubleshooting, and course corrections to make sure changes take hold and deliver the results your team expects.</p>
